{"tid":1558931,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"聽晚會唔會唱英文版國歌","createTime":"2019-09-10T15:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T00:46:21.000Z","uid":61499,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f921e9c09b23ed406605fe612dfd5e3b78c8129e","tid":1558931,"uid":61499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:24:51.000Z","msg":"話曬香港都係雙語城市, 兩個version都應該唱!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=koOAJHt9UO8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkoOAJHt9UO8&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4ZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=791a4a04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=koOAJHt9UO8</a><br />\n<br />\nFor the tears that we shed on this soil<br />\nFor the anguish we had in this turmoil<br />\nWe keep our heads up, our voices strong<br />\nMay freedom root in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nFor the fear that looms overhead<br />\nFor the hope that moves us ahead<br />\nWe march in blood, our martyrs along<br />\nMay freedom glow in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nDeepest night we shall not be in fright<br />\nIn the mist, a new day breaks with chants and light<br />\nStand with us, with virtuous minds and unbending spines<br />\nThe pearl we hold will always shine<br />\n<br />\nCome children of our motherland<br />\nThe time has come to wage a revolution<br />\nFreedom and liberty belong to this land<br />\nMay glory be to Hong Kong"},{"pid":"5a24cd7082f3ff1e265d11d41d7f444b9637498e","tid":1558931,"uid":61499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:26:29.000Z","msg":"推番上黎,我要攬炒!"},{"pid":"f2fff548c52d66bb28706aafa7372aee7b1a0a3d","tid":1558931,"uid":61499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:26:48.000Z","msg":"推番上黎,我要攬炒!"},{"pid":"997788a7bb9fc4513147be6185be36a3650dd44e","tid":1558931,"uid":61499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:27:10.000Z","msg":"推番上黎,我要攬炒!"},{"pid":"63971b9a90ae9b12d3b67154c521